## Code Formatting Tools

```
bash
# Black - The uncompromising code formatter
pip install black
black my_script.py

# isort - Sort and organize imports
pip install isort
isort my_script.py

# Use them together:
black my_script.py && isort my_script.py
```

## Linting Tools

```
bash
# Flake8 - Style guide enforcement
pip install flake8
